{"tid":1660163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去消委會投訴黨鐵?","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T10:56:45.000Z","uid":269629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4397db5a8c83e88893dc311bba489ab8443df1b6","tid":1660163,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"而家黨鐵全線十點收檔根本攞呢講，製造宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n買左全月通／都會票既，隨時夜晚無得搭，係限期內搭唔晒，蝕晒比黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n咁既情況，有無得去消委會投訴黨鐵貨要求回水？上次西鐵圍職員填form有無結果？唔可以就咁比黨鐵無原因咁提早收車。"},{"pid":"192a2a2d5869af2194cbee6561c4371be010b0ea","tid":1660163,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}